Quick Start

If you don't have another WebDesk, hit "No thanks".

To copy your data, just scan the QR code, or open Migrate on the other WebDesk, hit "Migrate", and enter this code:

8554170

Waiting for other WebDesk

Restoring from other WebDesk

Do not touch the other WebDesk, it could interrupt the copying process.

It's normal for this to take an unreasonable amount of time sometimes.

WebDesk Online services

WebDesk makes a DeskID for you. Others can use this ID to send you files or call you.

Keep your WebDesk open when possible. When WebDesk isn't open, anyone's able to take your DeskID and you can't receive things. You are your own server.

Create User

Data is stored on your device only. WebDesk does not collect any data from you. The name you enter is visible to anyone with your DeskID.
